# source
Informal conversion rules
-------------------------
                      
             +  
            / \         <-->    _+_ a b
           a   b

            var
           /            <-->    a var
          a

            ( )               
           / |          <-->    a ((_) b)
          a  b

         let in
        /   |  \        <-->    a (let_in_ b c)
       a    b   c

      if then else
     /  |    |    \     <-->    a (if_then_else_ b c d)
    a   b    c     d

 
